1.4.0.name: drupal/d4os_ui_auth

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

1.4.0.description: This module is managing user authentication by the website only, the grid only, or both. It is allowing you to synchronize users between grid and Drupal website. If a user is on the grid and not registered on the website, when the user tries to log in the website, his website account is created and vice versa.
